Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.60,manga,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz271.27\pos(1377,6)}沒有惡意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.60,manga,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz268.138\pos(1544,510)}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.60,manga,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz269.573\pos(1456,830)}我想說的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.60,manga,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz269.503\pos(1098,340)}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.60,manga,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270.761\pos(76,366)}你要我原諒那傢伙?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.60,manga,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz268.365\pos(138,934)}為什麼
